scene.message:
Ms. Natsumi: Hey,{nl}
what do you want to eat{nl}
tonight?{waitkey}{ret}

Her Boyfriend: You, of course!{nl}
Just kidding!{nl}
Nyahahaha!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Oh, Ms. Natsumi's{nl}
dream.{nl}
Then that must be the man{nl}
she broke up with recently.{waitkey}{clearbox}Not up to my standard, but{nl}
a decent-looking fellow.{nl}
Seems dim-witted, though.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Huh huh?{nl}
That's the boyfriend Ms.{nl}
Natsumi just split with?{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, not as good as me,{nl}
but he's doing pretty alright.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Kyaa!{nl}
The teacher's boyfriend{nl}
is super cool!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase wants a{nl}
boyfriend like that~{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Oh, you and your{nl}
jokes! Come on, what do you{nl}
want? Decide quick, quick.{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's hurry home and eat{nl}
our bento.{waitkey}{ret}

Her Boyfriend: Eh? Huh?{nl}
Didn't you say you'd cook{nl}
me your "homemade" food{waitkey}today, Natsumi??{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Oh dear, surely Ms.{nl}
Natsumi doesn't mean to pass{nl}
off a store bento as her{waitkey}{clearbox}"homemade" cooking and feed{nl}
it to him? Your Japanese is{nl}
all wrong, Ms. Natsumi.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Ms. Natsumi...{nl}
surely she doesn't mean to{nl}
call a bento bought here{waitkey}{clearbox}"homemade" and feed it to{nl}
him? Your use of Japanese{waitkey}is mistaken... Ms. Natsumi.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Yeah, I did!{nl}
Once we're at my place,{nl}
"I" will properly{waitkey}heat it in the microwave!{waitkey}{clearbox}How about this{nl}
"Surprise Cutlet Bento"?{nl}
It's a new product!{waitkey}Doesn't it look yummy!{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's get two of these!{nl}
Hey? Hey?{waitkey}{ret}

Her Boyfriend: ...uh...yeah{nl}
anything's... fine.{nl}
I'm just... so full up{waitkey}inside... heh heh...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Somehow... I can't{nl}
watch this, in many senses.{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's wake them quick{nl}
and hurry on.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Still, no wonder{nl}
the guy ran off on her.{nl}
That teacher...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hey,{nl}
the food here - is it okay{nl}
if Ayase and the others{waitkey}eat it, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: This is eerier than{nl}
a midnight convenience store{nl}
with no clerk or customers.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Wonder if I could{nl}
take this stuff back to the{nl}
real world...{nl}
what a waste.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Great!!{nl}
That the human power to dream{nl}
can create a space this Real!{waitkey}{clearbox}This convenience store is{nl}
the genuine article, any{nl}
way you look at it!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Hey!{nl}
What's with you?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Pull anything weird and{nl}
I'll call the police!!{waitkey}{ret}

Her Boyfriend: What the?{nl}
You! You got business{nl}
with us, huh?!{waitkey}{ret}
